*&quot;One Life to Live&quot; as Dr. Margaret &quot;Marty&quot; Saybrooke (1992–1997, 2004, 2005, 2008–2011)
*&quot;Zoya&quot; as Elizabeth (1995)
*&quot;Mrs. Winterbourne&quot; as Patricia Winterbourne (1996)
